RelatedSentence: Just after 4 a.m. Sunday , Velasquez was observed to be unconscious , with medical staff at the jail in Blountville immediately administering CPR .
She was then transported to Bristol Regional Medical Center by EMS and later pronounced dead .
In January , Velasquez was indicted by a Sullivan County grand jury , according to Sullivan County Assistant District Attorney Amy Hinkle , with the alleged incidents occurring in Bristol , Tenn .
